gtk2-perl: gtk2-perl (GTK+2/Cairo Bindings for Perl)
gtk2-perl:
gtk2-perl: gtk2-perl is a set of perl bindings for the GTK+2 library. These 
gtk2-perl: modules make it easy to write GTK and GNOME applications using 
gtk2-perl: Perl. It includes the Cairo and Gtk+2 bindings for perl.  It requires 
gtk2-perl: the glib-perl package.
